name: MindfulMixology

”Alexa, ask mindful mixology to find my orders”

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mindful mixology
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill is used to track order status for your Mindful Mixology Orders on an Alexa Device.
To use this skill you can say
Alexa, open mindful mixology followed by
 - Where's my stuff or What's my order status
